snippet: After Tim Tebow threw a long touchdown pass Wednesday, Rex Ryan said he doubted he would take any snaps with the Jets' starters in the first preseason game.
abstract: After Tim Tebow threw a long touchdown pass Wednesday, Rex Ryan said he doubted he would take any snaps with the Jets' starters in the first preseason game.

headline.main: Tebow Shines at Practice, Though Ryan Plays It Down
